    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The political, economic, and social principles advocated by Karl Marx, Friedrich Engels, and their followers; it includes the labor theory of value, dialectical materialism, economic determination of human actions, and class struggle as a fundamental force in history.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
